                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-262" type="given" value="DANIEL"></interp>DANIEL PAMPLET</persName>
                  </hi>. I received the prisoner in charge at the watch-house, and have the hat.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-263" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-263" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
