                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-263" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH MORRIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I was returning to my master's, and saw several young men about. I watched, and saw the prisoner take the hat from the shop—I took the hat up—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was very much in liquor.</p>
